OL,3,CIn pictures: Channel Islands celebrate
OL,4,C81st Liberation Day
OL,6,F81 years ago today, the Channel
OL,7,FIslands were freed after almost five
OL,8,Fyears of German Occupation.
OL,10,FPeople of all ages, including some who
OL,11,Flived in Jersey and Guernsey during
OL,12,Fthe Second World War, have been
OL,13,Fcelebrating in the streets and
OL,14,Fremembering one of the darkest
OL,15,Fchapters in our islands' shared
OL,16,Fhistory.
OL,18,FITV Channel is out and about in St
OL,19,FHelier and St Peter Port, capturing
OL,20,Fsome of the best moments from
OL,21,FLiberation Day.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/2
